message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY. The paper discusses the use of IBM Watson, a cognitive computing system, for question answering in natural languages. This falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
